data.description: This stunning property is located in the desirable Shallowbrook neighborhood in Dunlawton Hills, a community with its own swimming pool for residents. It is perfect for a first-time buyer, student, or empty nester. Enjoy the charming lake/pond view from the Florida room. The home has been recently renovated with a new roof, AC, and hot water heater, so you can move in with peace of mind. The kitchen is beautifully laid out with an island preparation area, and the dining room is spacious and versatile. It can be used as an office or converted into a third bedroom. This home is clean and ready for immediate occupancy. Don't miss this opportunity to own your dream home in Port Orange and you may even pay less than you would pay elsewhere in rent!
